					<br>
					<li style="color: black">원하는 캠핑 장소는?</li> <select
						style="width: 190px;">
						<option selected></option>
						<option value="mount">산</option>
						<option value="sea">바다</option>
					</select> <br>

					<li style="color: black">원하는 캠핑방식</li> <select
						style="width: 190px;">
						<option selected></option>
						<option value="car">차박</option>
